00:23:42,744 --> 00:23:43,824
<b><font color="#ffff00">But...</font></b>

364
00:23:44,784 --> 00:23:47,104
<b><font color="#ffff00">Is this enough to go to Canada?</font></b>

365
00:23:47,184 --> 00:23:48,344
<b><font color="#ffff00">Don't worry.</font></b>

366
00:23:48,424 --> 00:23:52,144
<b><font color="#ffff00">Si's family has a chalet mansion
with a very nice view in Canada.</font></b>

367
00:23:52,224 --> 00:23:53,864
<b><font color="#ffff00">Food and lodging would not be a problem.</font></b>

368
00:23:56,464 --> 00:23:59,384
<b><font color="#ffff00">Shancai, let's go with them.
I really want to go.</font></b>

369
00:24:03,304 --> 00:24:04,784
<b><font color="#ffff00"><i>I want to go too.</i></font></b>

370
00:24:05,304 --> 00:24:06,224
<b><font color="#ffff00"><i>But...</i></font></b>

371
00:24:06,624 --> 00:24:08,664
<b><font color="#ffff00"><i>Daoming Si would probably be there too.</i></font></b>

372
00:24:09,784 --> 00:24:11,904
<b><font color="#ffff00"><i>We had such a big fight.</i></font></b>

373
00:24:12,344 --> 00:24:15,224
<b><font color="#ffff00"><i>How can I pretend like nothing happened</i></font></b>

374
00:24:16,504 --> 00:24:18,344
<b><font color="#ffff00"><i>and stay at his mansion?</i></font></b>

375
00:24:24,984 --> 00:24:27,304
<b><font color="#ffff00">-I'm home.
-You're back?</font></b>

376
00:24:30,344 --> 00:24:31,224
<b><font color="#ffff00">Shancai.</font></b>

377
00:24:31,984 --> 00:24:34,184
<b><font color="#ffff00">I heard that you're going to Canada
in a couple of days.</font></b>

378
00:24:34,824 --> 00:24:37,304
<b><font color="#ffff00">Remember to buy smoked salmon for me.</font></b>

379
00:24:37,864 --> 00:24:39,784
<b><font color="#ffff00">Yes. And maple syrup.</font></b>

380
00:24:39,944 --> 00:24:41,144
<b><font color="#ffff00">Buy a few bottles.</font></b>

381
00:24:41,344 --> 00:24:43,784
<b><font color="#ffff00">I heard the stewed chicken leg
